00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:05.380
Hola, vicepresidente Qian.

00:00:05.380 --> 00:00:08.508
Soy Zhang Jian Bin,
un reportero de la revista semanal.

00:00:08.508 --> 00:00:09.926
